00:10:50,576 --> 00:10:54,779
It's slightly fantastic, but the proportions are still semi-realistic.

212
00:10:54,779 --> 00:10:59,501
And the palette overall for both of the images, both Keith Parkinson and Larry Elmore, is

213
00:10:59,501 --> 00:11:00,242
relatively subdued.

214
00:11:00,242 --> 00:11:05,024
You don't get a lot of really intense colors like you might see in a lot of contemporary

215
00:11:05,024 --> 00:11:05,405
fantasy art.

216
00:11:06,554 --> 00:11:08,636
And we wanted to capture the classic isometric look

217
00:11:08,636 --> 00:11:09,437
and feel.

218
00:11:09,437 --> 00:11:10,838
And as I'll show in the next image,

