00:11:15,001 --> 00:11:16,483
but we came close.

221
00:11:16,483 --> 00:11:17,904
Baldur's Gate 2 in Icewind Dale.

222
00:11:17,904 --> 00:11:20,866
Baldur's Gate 2, that's a straight render.

223
00:11:20,866 --> 00:11:23,729
The image from Icewind Dale, it was heavily painted over.

224
00:11:23,729 --> 00:11:25,330
That's something that Black Isle did

225
00:11:25,330 --> 00:11:27,392
that I don't think Bioware really did at all.

226
00:11:27,392 --> 00:11:30,635
At Black Isle, we usually did a lot of painting on our images

227
00:11:30,635 --> 00:11:32,997
after we rendered them and got in a lot of cool painterly

228
00:11:32,997 --> 00:11:33,497
details.

229
00:11:35,035 --> 00:11:37,237
So for Pillars of Eternity's isometric style,

230
00:11:37,237 --> 00:11:40,800
we wanted to add dynamic lighting.

