00:47:33,881 --> 00:47:37,703
on these murder hobos that wander the world just acquiring

917
00:47:37,703 --> 00:47:38,283
power and loot.

918
00:47:38,283 --> 00:47:41,484
So yeah, there's a ton of really cool games

919
00:47:41,484 --> 00:47:43,885
out there that I think we can borrow elements from.

